@BarKeep
#end
:touch
Hey, you're a merc ain't cha? Listen bud,
I got a job for you. I need you to smuggle
some weapons to the planet Ekul, where
there's a civil war going on between the
Ekul Rebels, and the Government. It'll be
a dangerous job, and you'll be stopped
along the way. But I'll pay you a lot. All
told you'll get 5000 credits, and a heavy
chain cannon. What do you say?
!2;Okay.
!1;No.
#end
:1
Fine. But remember, there ain't that much
work around for mercenaries these days.
I doubt you'll be able to find another
customer all too soon.
#end
:2
#zap touch
Great! You'll get 2000 credits in advance,
the rest you'll get after you deliver the
goods. When you reach Ekul find the Rebel
known as the Skorpian, and give him the
stuff. If you want you can work for him
too you know. Just remember one thing,
$Any and all
$who dare to cross
$Skorpian's lot
$shall feel his bite
#give score 2000
#send Thug:ok
#end

    end
